{
  "stem": "2460.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them, most of the things we did not believe what is happening, because we just couldn't believe that those things that the Polish children-- they ran away from some camps, concentration camps, and ended up in our city, two of them, in 1942.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told us horror stories that even the rabbi, Saturday in the shul, told us that we shouldn't believe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those are gypsy children, and the stories are just not true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, those were Jewish-Polish children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for some reason, the Hungarians and the Polish, they didn't like each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For some reason, they called them gypsies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is what I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, those children, I went to-- to school together with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was 1942 when those two children arrived in our city.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one Jewish family without children took them in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- they went to school with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when they arrived, they told us, when they already learned the Hungarian language, they told us that their family, the entire [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jewish population from their town, was herded to a synagogue, and they were burned alive.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was very hard to believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But if I remember, they were crying when they told us those stories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we didn't believe them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember their names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were given Hungarian names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their original names, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we just went to the same school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- they were older than I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to the same school, so I remember, they went to school with us, and they went back to Auschwitz with us and probably didn't even survive.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they arrived, they were children of 14, probably 14, 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Poland, they came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
